articles.description: Alessandro Lever scored 29 points and Damari Milstead sank two free throws with 21 seconds remaining as third-seeded Grand Canyon recovered from first-half jitters in the school's first trip to the post season and defeat No. 5 seed Missouri-Kansas...
articles.headline: Grand Canyon wins first post-season game, downs UMKC 77-74

articles.description: T.J. Shorts II scored 15 points, including the clinching free throws with one second left, Joe Mooney had a career-high 15 points and top-seeded UC Davis edged eighth-seeded UC Riverside 70-66 on Thursday in the opening game of the Big West Conference...
articles.headline: Shorts, Mooney lead Davis over Riverside 70-66 in BWC opener

articles.description: Allonzo Trier scores 22 points as Arizona defeats Colorado 83-67.
articles.headline: Arizona cruises past Colorado

images.caption: Allonzo Trier scores 22 points as Arizona defeats Colorado 83-67.
images.name: Arizona cruises past Colorado

articles.description: Potential lottery pick Michael Porter Jr. looked a little rusty in his first game action since mid-November.
articles.headline: Michael Porter Jr. a little off in return from back surgery

images.caption: Michael Porter Jr. scores 12 points in his first game back, but the Tigers fall to Georgia, 62-60 in the SEC tournament.
images.name: Missouri falls in Porter's return

articles.description: Kansas tops Oklahoma State 82-68 behind Malik Newman's career-high 30 points.
articles.headline: Newman's career day lifts Kansas

articles.description: Yante Maten scored 21 points and grabbed 10 rebounds and Georgia spoiled the return of heralded freshman Michael Porter Jr. with a in a 62-60 victory over Missouri in the second round of the Southeastern Conference Tournament on Thursday.
articles.headline: Georgia spoils Porter Jr.'s return, beats Missouri 62-60

images.caption: Forward Yante Maten reflects on Georgia's gutsy win over Missouri and what he told his team down the stretch that helped lead to the victory.
images.name: Maten: 'We're a tremendous team'
